reviewText: I was so very glad to by this Blu-Ray movie because, I love watching the very hot young women on set!!! Lorissa McComas, is so very hot and sexy in this film!!!
Lorissa was extremely beautiful, but this Blu-ray did not do her justice.  There are a lot better footage of her out there and cheaper.
Cute but not quite on the spot. Pic quality oldish and not on par with bluray era. Take this if you have a soft spot for this particular female. Otherwise maybe not.
